Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  那么我要上喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  从我开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.77,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,140)\fad(0,600)}格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.77,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,140)\fad(0,600)}力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.77,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,140)\fad(0,600)}高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}格力高：也就是日本江崎格力高食品公司，著名产品有pocky，相信大家不会陌生。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pi～ne～app～le～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我来喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  一层一层上可是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格～力～高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的附～赠～品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能擅自加字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不是一般都要加个赠品的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50比50
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你要是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要发动自己的规则了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一个轮到麻衣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちよた　みけら　はとほ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,らすて　のはて　きらと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なりは　してと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:19.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注释见后文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是复活的咒语
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过7点钟要把我喊起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和街道委员会的人们去玩藤球了  by妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}藤球：由东南亚的"sepak raga"运动起源的用头和脚传递使球不落地的运动。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤…藤球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.06,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N5
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  今天可是我值日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟为什么偏偏今天就没有电池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完了的话就应该提前跟我说「用完了」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨蛋闹钟！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之只能以全速跑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:04:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话总会有办法…话说回来  刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个很奇怪的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它…追来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀什么呀  这场赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要追我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  稍微打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个木鱼是你掉的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这个金木鱼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被杀掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配合的话  就要被杀掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我是只熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有时候我…还是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我的真面目是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵  正确答案是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我穿着美绪的校服所以没认出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  难得一大早就能看到如此漂亮的飞旋拳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  真的非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我可是累死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把那个闹钟弄停可费了大劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  别那么生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我来请你吃拉面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是野口英世，印在1000円上的日本著名医学家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的野口！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.70,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,250)\fad(600,0)}咒\N语
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所谓的咒语其实是FC上用来代替存档的密码，且正确的密码其实是\Nちよた みけら はとほ らすて のはて きらと なには してと，来源于DQ2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,220)}咒语输入错误
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.36,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N6
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鲨鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  那片云  好像鲨鱼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  哪一片？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我牛奶买回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…4.5  4.5的纯牛奶  4.5的纯牛奶  4.5！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}好  是特浓的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}但是怎么了  突然间想喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有夹心蛋糕卷可以吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,335)}roll cake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以随便地改造我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夹心蛋糕卷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！  4.5的纯牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么4.5的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得手臂里装着夹心蛋糕卷而生活下去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈  凉凉的好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要是这被外面的谁看到了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜咕噜咕噜～咕噜噜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  也给我喝一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  夹心蛋糕卷也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}甜面包：日文叫做「甘食」，甜味的伞状面包。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  就给你吃点甜面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缩回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  我按错键了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你又要做这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不小心在外面启动了的话会变成什么样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}桑勃：源自俄罗斯的格斗技，类似柔道，也加入了擒拿术等综合格斗技。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑勃摔跤指挥官真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你加个音乐播放机能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢  为什么要向改造方向发展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好听我说话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足的一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  因为博士你已经吃了夹心蛋糕卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你好了  反正我还有年轮蛋糕可以吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:17.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,335)}Baumkuchen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又在我的身体里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还是下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请一开始就全部放到冰箱里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你满满的能量哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美绪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笑脸是要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又忘记做作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这可真是不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  总是这样话考试又会很惨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次  就这次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一次了  拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  之前你就已经说过这话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士绝不食言！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你早就已经食言了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这次了哦  真的最后一次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我能仰仗的就只有美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  刚才我说的做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我抄好了的话就马上还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  让我看让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  我是不是忘记什么东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上做完作业后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完作业后…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随手画的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随手画的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不允许你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.02,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,300)\fad(600,600)\bord10\shad0\be50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来我自己也忘了写作业了  真是失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  把笔记还给我吧  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  我都说了看了也没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来又来  真是的  别耍那一套了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过下次我一定会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办了  这下可惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是看到那个的话  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会被奇怪的眼光看待的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且看到那幅画的人  偏偏是祐子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那种传播力可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音速级别！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  那…那是国语的笔记本  数学的在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本子上：数学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:53.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本子上：每日日记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这上面写了是数学的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我肚子很痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会抄好的  稍微等一下下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了  要是在这里被看到的话  我就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中生活就结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  那本笔记  我用一千円买！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  不是那样  那本笔记会…  那本笔记会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会爆炸啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追不上奔跑着的祐子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了  我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:16:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  我的人生  到现在都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有些不如意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总的来说  是场幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都完了  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生…和男人们的盛宴一起结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对！不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧…生命吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}暂停成功\N「ナタデココ」椰浆果冻，椰子汁发酵的凝胶状食品起源于菲律宾，也是演员水沢奈子的爱称。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:35.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里奔跑的场景人物线条用的都是原作里的作画风格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…我也够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在…走廊上奔跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从后面把笔记传上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有忘记写作业的家伙们快点自己承认哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时间还真不知道会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好总算是平安无事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能回到我的日常生活了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是忘记擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  长野原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}目标：伴着汗水的无悔青春  1年Q班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我忘记写作业了！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.81,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,300)\fad(600,0)}收\N拾\N屋\N子\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  请稍微收拾下屋子里的垃圾好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对博士来说这或许还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.64,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,300)\fad(0,600)}学\N生\N指\N导
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那时候  我对那家伙说了3999…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  抱歉  安中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:22.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在走廊上请勿急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是有一点点啦  你的发饰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太大了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像兔子一样？
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.45,-0:00:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.99,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,280)\fad(0,0)}甜\N面\N包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜面包真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}便利店招牌：春季的笔头草便当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}商品售罄  令人怀念的甜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}店长推荐：廉价装甜面包，大人气，多到突破天际的分量，55个装，超好吃。
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.72,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原  你有没有作为文化祭执行委员的自觉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微认真地考虑下会怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都非常认真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为戏剧部部长就要经常融入各色角色之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点都不知道吗  立花美里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂你个头啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}好好听我说话!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上我们差不多该决定文化祭的摆摊事项了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的戏剧部一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换商标了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我和这家伙分到一组了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑道部的比赛也要临近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}Helvetica Standard日常原作者あらゐけいいち以自己的同人社团「ヒマラヤイルカ」的名义创作的同人志\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:21:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  现在真不想当什么文化祭执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:08.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}翘起小指是笹原的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  还看什么漫画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快点提出方案的话  我们不都回不了家了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  因为是新刊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有一个方案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前提出的葡萄酒品尝大赛不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行  驳回哟  驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级驳回！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  笹原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  刚才开始就在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我稍微有点用脑过度想不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  笹原  你要去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来她今天的心情相当不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说葡萄酒品尝大赛已经是非常完美的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙从开始到现在完全都没有提出方案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我这样和她说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会没命的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是如果我不提出方案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就没办法回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非得要我把思考方式降到庶民级别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我就稍微认真地考虑下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你可没有任何意思哦！
